# Results Directory

This directory stores training outputs, plots, and analysis results.

## Typical Contents

- `training_progress.png` - Learning curves showing score over episodes
- `ConvergenceGraph.png` - Q-value convergence visualization
- `AnimatedGames.gif` - Animated gameplay at different training stages
- Training logs and statistics

## Generated Files

Files in this directory are automatically generated during training and can be regenerated at any time.
